  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;Transport &amp; Environment (T&amp;E)&#xA0;works toward a healthier climate and environment in the European Union. It plans to work with various environmental organizations &#x2014; including Deutsche Umwelthilfe and Naturschutzbund Deutschland in Germany, Milieudefensie in the Netherlands, Legambiente in Italy, and Ecologistas en Acci&#xF3;n in Spain &#x2014; to build a more diverse, equitable, and inclusive (DEI) climate movement. T&amp;E will support human resources policies to hire and train ethnically diverse staff, distribute research and survey findings on DEI in the E.U. climate movement, and raise awareness of DEI in the European environmental community. (Substrategy: Climate Finance)&quot;</narrative>
  </description>
